          <h2 style="color: #5CC05C;">3. Explore Scenarios</h2>
          <p>Filter by scenario using the <code style="background: #333; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;">demo_id</code> field:</p>
          <pre style="background: #1a1a1a; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; overflow-x: auto;">
# Find all exfil scenario events
